 wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth G. Gatzka was born in 1272, in Germany. She had at least 1 son with Thomas G. Cox. She died in 1350, in her hometown, at the age of 78."},"et":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1342":"1342","1350":"1350","1272":"1272","1270":"1270","England":"England","Germany":"Saksamaa"},"fi":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1342":"1342","1350":"1350","1272":"1272","1270":"1270","England":"England","Germany":"Saksa"},"fr":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1342":"1342","1350":"1350","1272":"1272","1270":"1270","England":"Angleterre","Germany":"Allemagne","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth G. Gatzka est née en 1272, à Allemagne. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Thomas G. Cox. Elle est décédée en 1350, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 78 ans."},"de":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1342":"1342","1350":"1350","1272":"1272","1270":"1270","England":"England","Germany":"Deutschland","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth G. Gatzka wurde 1272 in Deutschland geboren. Sie hatte mit Thomas G. Cox mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb 1350 im Alter von 78 Jahren in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1342":"1342","1350":"1350","1272":"1272","1270":"1270","England":"England","Germany":"Allemagne"},"hu":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"1379","1300":"1300","1342":"1342","1350":"1350","1272":"1272","1270":"1270","England":"England","Germany":"Németország"},"id":{"1272–1350":"1272–1350","1270–1342":"1270–1342","1300–1379":"1300–1379","1379":"